%20automated%20palletizer%20works%20in%20a%20facility.%3Cp%3EFormic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20trade%20war%20has%20increased%20demand%20for%20robotics%20and%20automation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERobots-as-a-service%20company%20Formic%20said%20its%20customers%20have%20stepped%20up%20their%20use%20of%20robots%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAutomation%20can%20help%20companies%20to%20save%20money%20amid%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAutomation%20company%20Formic%20said%20that%20its%20customers%20stepped%20up%20their%20robot%20usage%20this%20year%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-news-tech-sector-trump-announces-tariff-exemptions-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20announcements%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20global%20supply%20chains%20into%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormic%20automates%20packing%20and%20palletizing%20%E2%80%94%20or%20placing%20packages%20on%20a%20pallet%20%E2%80%94%20for%20automotive%2C%20industrial%2C%20food%2C%20beverage%2C%20and%20consumer%20packaged%20goods%20companies.%20It%20operates%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Brobots-as-a-service%26quot%3B%20model%2C%20meaning%20that%20customers%20lease%20Formic's%20robots%20and%20pay%20a%20monthly%20rate%20based%20on%20how%20much%20they%20use%20them.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIts%20robots%20are%20deployed%20in%20more%20than%20100%20factories%20in%20the%20US%20and%20have%20stacked%20and%20packed%20more%20than%201.2%20billion%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20January%20and%20February%2C%20Formic's%20customers%20increased%20their%20robot%20usage%20by%20more%20than%2017%25%20overall%2C%20Chief%20Marketing%20Officer%20Shawn%20Fitzgerald%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Its%20food%20and%20beverage%20customers%20stepped%20up%20their%20usage%20by%20more%20than%2013%25.%20He%20said%20the%20usage%20numbers%20seemed%20particularly%20notable%20given%20that%20February%20has%20fewer%20business%20days%20than%20the%20other%20months%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20that%20brands%20were%20using%20robots%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20any%20tariff-related%20price%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20his%20first%20in%20a%20series%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-plan-deadline-trade-policies-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20announcements%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%201%2C%20placing%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20China%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Mexico%2C%20and%20closing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ede%20minimis%20tax%20loophole%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20data%20suggests%20everyone%20sat%20down%20with%20each%20other%20and%20said%2C%20let's%20step%20on%20the%20gas%20as%20much%20as%20we%20can%20in%20February%2C%20and%20let's%20make%20as%20much%20as%20we%20possibly%20can%20at%20the%20price%20points%20we%20are%20at%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Fitzgerald%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormic%20customers'%20robot%20usage%20dipped%20in%20March%2C%20but%20the%20numbers%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20a%20rebound%20so%20far%20in%20April%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20This%20month%20has%20seen%20the%20return%20of%20global%20trade%20chaos%20as%20Trump%20announced%20a%20large%20set%20of%20tariffs%20on%20April%202%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20then%20later%20paused%20those%20tariffs%20except%20for%20those%20on%20goods%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitzgerald%20said%20that%20working%20with%20Formic%20helps%20companies%20to%20get%20more%20predictability%20in%20their%20costs%20amid%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20unfortunately%20have%20to%20go%20to%20overtime%2C%20robots%20love%20first%2C%20second%2C%20and%20third%20shift%20and%20overtime%20all%20the%20same.%20They%20do%20not%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220101d9ed-679c-4f98-8799-633d53bfc6fe%5C%22%3EUsing%20automation%20to%20'fill%20in%20some%20of%20the%20gaps'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFormic's%20customers%20include%20Rumiano%20Cheese%20Company%2C%20a%20cheese-making%20and%20packaging%20company%20based%20in%20Willows%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20the%20Sacramento%20Valley%20of%20California.%20Automation%20is%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20the%20106-year-old%20company%20%E2%80%94%20even%20more%20so%20as%20tariffs%20have%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20profits%20this%20year.%20Rumiano%20imports%20cheeses%20from%20Italy%20and%20exports%20products%20to%20Mexico%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20through%20a%20third%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERumiano%20is%20installing%20a%20Formic%20robot%20that%20can%20pick%20up%2030-pound%20boxes%20of%20cheese%20and%20move%20them%20from%20the%20production%20line%20to%20pallets%20to%20be%20shipped%20out%20to%20customers.%20But%20Formic's%20robots%20are%20just%20one%20of%20several%20automation%20solutions%20Rumiano%20has%20explored.%20It%20also%20uses%20a%20machine%20that%20puts%20stacks%20of%20cheese%20in%20the%20proper%20place%20so%20they%20can%20be%20packaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacks%20of%20cheese%20are%20lifted%20by%20robotic%20arms%20in%20Rumiano%20cheese%20facility%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd6aba3fe8d3928363096a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStacks%20of%20cheese%20are%20lifted%20by%20robotic%20arms%20inside%20Rumiano's%20facility.%3Cp%3ERumiano%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20more%20AI%20and%20robotics%20conversations%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%20than%20we've%20probably%20had%20in%20the%20year%20prior%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Henson%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20operations%20at%20Rumiano.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20who%20previously%20stacked%20cheese%20by%20hand%20have%20been%20reassigned%20to%20other%20tasks%20in%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20robotics%20and%20data%20partners%20is%20key%20for%20the%20small%2C%20family-owned%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20teams%20of%20data%20scientists%20or%20anything%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Wolper%2C%20director%20of%20planning%20at%20Rumiano%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20to%20partners%20to%20help%20us%20grow%20with%20AI%20tools%20to%20help%20us%20really%20dig%20into%20data%20so%20that%20we%20can%20make%20sure%20we're%20spending%20money%20on%20the%20right%20things%2C%20we're%20producing%20the%20right%20products%2C%20we're%20doing%20everything%20as%20efficiently%20as%20we%20can%20to%20help%20save%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20have%20created%20obvious%20challenges%20for%20brands%2C%20but%20supply%20chain%20optimization%20has%20been%20a%20hot%20topic%20for%20several%20years.%20It's%20an%20area%20where%20robots%20and%20software%20can%20help%2C%20Forrester%20analyst%20Paul%20Miller%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Covid%20there%20has%20been%20this%20broad%20idea%20about%20shortening%20supply%20chains%2C%20improving%20resilience%2C%20improving%20adaptability%2C%20and%20part%20of%20that%20is%20bringing%20manufacturing%20capacity%20closer%20to%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20trying%20to%20bring%20that%20manufacturing%20capacity%20to%20California%20or%20Germany%20or%20Japan%2C%20the%20people%20are%20not%20cheap.%20You%20need%20to%20use%20automation%20to%20fill%20in%20some%20of%20the%20gaps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20alluded%20to%20this%20idea%20in%20several%20TV%20appearances%20he%20made%20after%20Trump%20announced%20his%20ta