onsidered%20a%20new%20concept%20in%20India%2C%20and%20Deeksha%20considers%20herself%20fortunate%20to%20have%20been%20getting%20orders%20through%20social%20media%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20her%20first%20painting%20of%20a%20black%20and%20white%20tiger%2C%20Deeksha%20has%20two%20favourites%20to%20date.%20%E2%80%9COne%20is%20a%20five-by-three%20feet%20hyper-realistic%20painting%20of%20a%20tiger.%20The%20painting%20took%20around%20three%20months%3B%20I%20am%20still%20looking%20for%20the%20right%20buyer%20who%20would%20give%20the%20respect%20the%20painting%20deserves%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-14T191031.738-1744638044-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-420145%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDeeksha%20shares%20that%20people%20often%20say%20her%20paintings%20look%20like%20photographs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20a%203D%20painting%20of%20a%20Rhinoceros%20(30%C3%9740%20inches)%2C%20and%20when%20she%20posted%20it%20on%20Facebook%2C%20many%20people%20commented%20that%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20photograph.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20paintings%20may%20sometimes%20look%20like%20they%20were%20AI-generated%2C%20but%20they%20are%20purely%20hand-painted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deeksha%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishith%20Kumar%2C%20a%20pulmonologist%20from%20Ranchi%20and%20one%20of%20Deeksha%E2%80%99s%20clients%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20able%20to%20replicate%20the%20exact%20reference%20images%20I%20had%20sent%2C%20and%20she%20constantly%20updated%20me%20on%20her%20progress.%20Most%20of%20the%20individuals%20who%20walk%20into%20my%20chamber%20look%20at%20the%20painting%20and%20ask%2C%20%E2%80%98Who%20clicked%20this%20picture%3F%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looks%20incredibly%20realistic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Deeksha%20works%20every%20day%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efine-tune%20her%20artistic%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20her%20main%20focus%20lies%20in%20giving%20back%20to%20animals%20through%20art.%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20with%20the%20money%20earned%20from%20art%2C%20I%20donate%20to%20people%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20animal%20conservation%20on%20a%20small%20scale%20to%20support%20their%20initiatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20paint%20into%20purpose%20(and%20a%20paycheck)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20full-time%20artist%20comes%20with%20uncertainties%2C%20and%20Deeksha%20has%20made%20lifestyle%20changes%20to%20sustain%20herself%20without%20depending%20on%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20I%20earn%2C%20very%20little%20goes%20into%20my%20personal%20expenses%2C%20which%20are%20primarily%20art%20supplies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20The%20rest%20is%20spent%20on%20supporting%20animals%20and%20birds%20whenever%20she%20gets%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20to%20travel%20solo%2C%20and%20even%20while%20doing%20so%2C%20I%20opt%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20locals%20instead%20of%20luxury%20stays.%20In%20return%2C%20I%20do%20something%20for%20them%20by%20teaching%20their%20children%20about%20insects%2C%20wildlife%2C%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20not%20harming%20any%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeeksha%20refrains%20from%20staying%20in%20one%20place%2C%20believing%20that%20travelling%20enhances%20her%20creativity%2C%20thereby%20improving%20her%20art.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20teacher%20has%20also%20been%20nature%2C%20and%20I%20have%20trained%20myself%20to%20spot%20the%20tiniest%20of%20details%20to%20add%20realistic%20elements.%20But%20wherever%20I%20go%2C%20I%20carry%20my%20art%20supplies%20and%20continue%20creating%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20the%20wildlife%20experience%20to%20everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Deeksha%2C%20every%20painting%20is%20a%20labour%20of%20love%2C%20shaped%20with%20patience%20and%20precision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20paintings%20that%20I%20make%20for%20myself%20take%20one%20to%20four%20months%20depending%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414852%2Fkashmiri-artist-bone-art-aziz-ul-rehman-sustainable-art%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20intricacies%20involved.%3C%2Fa%3E%20For%20commissioned%20orders%2C%20I%20try%20to%20provide%20them%20according%20to%20the%20discussed%20timeline%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deeksha%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20has%20painted%20on%20diverse%20surfaces%20like%20traditional%20canvases%2C%20tote%20bags%2C%20and%20even%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20Deeksha%20has%20sold%2050%20paintings%2C%20re